name: Tetris Movie 1
description:
Tetris Movie 1, from "North by Northwest" (1959), by Alfred Hitchcock
Replay of the most famous scene of "North by Northwest"

“Oh, well a cut is nothing. One cut of film is like a piece of mosaic. To me, pure film, pure cinema is pieces of film assembled. Any individual piece is nothing. But a combination of them creates an idea.” Alfred Hitchcock
